--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Steps to run uqpce_wrapper:

1) have a input.yaml file in your directory
	- make sure all UQPCE Settings are specified in this file

2) set EXECPATH variable
	- path to the executable
		
3) add PCE_Codes to your PATH and PYTHONPATH

4) add uqpce_wrapper to your PATH and PYTHONPATH

5) run "python -m uqpce_wrapper"

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Example (bash):

	export EXECPATH="/home/myname/bin/executable"
	export PATH="/home/myname/dir_to_PCE_Codes:$PATH"
	export PYTHONPATH="/home/myname/dir_to_PCE_Codes:$PYTHONPATH"
	export PATH="/home/myname/dir_to_uqpce_wrapper:$PATH"
	export PYTHONPATH="/home/myname/dir_to_uqpce_wrapper:$PYTHONPATH"

	python -m uqpce_wrapper

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To run the UQPCE example that generates the results from UQPCE, follow the 
instructions and set EXECPATH to "uqpce_wrapper/execute_uqpce.py".

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------